<h4>Description</h4>
<p>This package is for yalu + mach_portal &amp; Extra_recipe &amp; Electra &amp; unc0ver &amp; chackra1n &amp; Odyssey etc.</p>
<strong style="color: #f00;">First, delete the OTA data.</strong>
<p>Settings -&gt; General -&gt; Strage &amp; iCloud Usage -&gt; Manage Storage</p>
<p>tvOS beta profile and Reboot is not required.</p>
<strong style="color: #f00;">Cydia Substrate is required to erase the badge.</strong>
<strong style="color: #f00;">For iOS 12.2 unc0ver, please turn off "Disable Updates".</strong>
<p>Once put a badge on the software update of the Settings app, try ldrestart or userspace reboot or reboot.</p>
<strong style="color: #f00;">Re-enable OTA updates</strong>
<p>Run the following after removing the package</p>
<ul>
<li>launchctl reboot userspace</li>
<li>reboot</li>
</ul>
<p>PowerSelector recommended</p>
